          </TextReveal>

          <TextReveal delay={200} client:load>
            <div class="testimonial-card">
              <div class="quote-icon">"</div>
              <p class="testimonial-text">
                Unravel.tech built our complete event-ingestion pipeline for Espressif chips, handling API servers, Kafka, and MongoDB. Their distributed systems expertise let me focus on business outcomes - a partnership we'll gladly continue.
              </p>
              <div class="testimonial-author">
