                  </svg>
                  LinkedIn
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </TextReveal>

          <TextReveal delay={300} client:load>
            <div class="testimonial-card">
              <div class="quote-icon">"</div>
              <p class="testimonial-text">
                I'm confident in Unravel's ability to effectively deliver any project they commit to. They are excellent product engineers and understand what solving a real customer pain-point and delivering business outcomes is.
              </p>
              <div class="testimonial-author">
                <div class="author-name">Akshay Vaidya</div>
                <div class="author-title">Advisor to Startups, Angel Investor</div>
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/akshay-vaidya-908702/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="author-linkedin">
                  <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                    <path d="M19 0h-14c-2.761 0-5 2.239-5 5v14c0 2.761 2.239 5 5 5h14c2.762 0 5-2.239 5-5v-14c0-2.761-2.238-5-5-5zm-11 19h-3v-11h3v11zm-1.5-12.268c-.966 0-1.75-.79-1.75-1.764s.784-1.764 1.75-1.764 1.75.79 1.75 1.764-.783 1.764-1.75 1.764zm13.5 12.268h-3v-5.604c0-3.368-4-3.113-4 0v5.604h-3v-11h3v1.765c1.396-2.586 7-2.777 7 2.476v6.759z"/>
